J. Larson, D. Pujara, D. Ramirez, L. Miller, T. Patel, N. Babar, A. Spanias, “WIP: Building a Research Experience for Undergraduates in Quantum Machine Learning” 2024 Frontiers in Education (FIE), Washington DC, USA.
